@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.92) * 0.02) * wp.exp((v1 + 0.16 / tmp + 0.85)))
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.59)) - 0.82)
    v0 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.38 - v1 + 0.55) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.31)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
